{"tid":2207684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"還押近三周　中六男生認藏醋、酒精　判入更生中心","createTime":"2020-09-18T10:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T12:55:23.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76c3d49c9d3b3f42fb4d40d0275d38f9842823b7","tid":2207684,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:27:16.000Z","msg":"兩名 16 歲學生去年 11 月觀塘警署遭警截查後，逃跑其中一人涉扔下一樽稀釋食用醋，兩人跑至觀塘游泳池外終被截停，在背囊中再搜出一樽酒精。男生早前承認一項串謀意圖施用有害物品使人受損害、精神受創或惱怒，還押至今近三周，案件今（18日）在觀塘裁判法院判刑。主任裁判官徐綺薇指，考慮被告年紀較輕，勇於承擔過錯，學業成績優異，但因控罪嚴重，刑罰須具阻嚇性，以防止後來者作出相關行為，為社會及被告利益著想，最終判被告入更生中心。"},{"pid":"33ee1297169d0b03fc7a70d0ed70119cddf2a372","tid":2207684,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%89%E5%91%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%AD%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E8%97%8F%E9%86%8B-%E9%85%92%E7%B2%BE-%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E6%9B%B4%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2591%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25AD%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2586%258B-%25E9%2585%2592%25E7%25B2%25BE-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdaZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=61e8e5a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2591%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25AD%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2586%258B-%25E9%2585%2592%25E7%25B2%25BE-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&h=679328fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%89%E5%91%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%AD%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E8%97%8F%E9%86%8B-%E9%85%92%E7%B2%BE-%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E6%9B%B4%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</a>"},{"pid":"d39aae39933333827f066d100cd4a2bba1ae5076","tid":2207684,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"她表示，被告無過往定罪記錄，勇於承擔過錯，最終判他入更生中心；最低刑期為 3 個月，而最高刑期為 9 個月。"},{"pid":"a7542d60c75316481d68b79b2f311f3b37d90d3e","tid":2207684,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50b72788c2ad2b711fbb3f8121697be7836705c","tid":2207684,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689ec8d52d95e3de8b2cc99dda96d6e5ee7a3403","tid":2207684,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbb82a3db59df7c6701832d1f22fc7f7ff55e1f","tid":2207684,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:31:04.000Z","msg":"警署外被截藏食用醋及酒精 16歲男生認罪還柙候判<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2184045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2184045</a><br />\n<br />\n男被告警誡下稱，透過網上學習將酒精和醋混合，準備拿給手足使用；其手提電話的對話內容提及，有女子曾與案發前一晚問男被告拿漂白水，稱準備帶往狗屋做試驗。"},{"pid":"04f0bcaaab7aeb57fee659b7d03c18625d64b031","tid":2207684,"uid":1818,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:31:42.000Z","msg":"如果企定定<br />\n等到律師到先落口供<br />\n會唔會結果已經唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f95c1a18d1133d65615c103